'''塔内希·马茂'''（[[吉里巴斯語|吉里巴斯語]]：{{lang|gil|Taneti Maamau}}；{{bd|1960年|9月16日}}），是一名[[基里巴斯|基里巴斯]]政治家，自2016年3月11日擔任[[基里巴斯總統|基里巴斯總統]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=345056 |title=Taneti Maamau declared new president of Kiribati - Fiji Times Online |website=Fijitimes.com |date= |accessdate=2016-03-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311133005/http://www.fijitimes.com/story.aspx?id=345056 |archivedate=2016-03-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.tahiti-infos.com/Kiribati-un-nouveau-president-elu-a-la-place-d-un-champion-de-la-cause-climatique_a145731.html |title=Kiribati: un nouveau président élu à la place d'un champion de la cause climatique |website=Tahiti-infos.com |date= |accessdate=2016-03-13 |archive-date=2016-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311131310/http://www.tahiti-infos.com/Kiribati-un-nouveau-president-elu-a-la-place-d-un-champion-de-la-cause-climatique_a145731.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时兼任该国外交部长<ref>{{cite news |title=王毅会见基里巴斯总统兼外长马茂 |url=https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/wjbzhd/t1702045.shtml |accessdate=2019-09-29 |publisher=中华人民共和国外交部 |date=2019-09-26 |archive-date=2019-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926045650/https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/wjbzhd/t1702045.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

他是[[2016年基里巴斯總統選舉|2016年基里巴斯總統選舉]]中唯一反對黨的候選人<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.pina.com.fj/?p=pacnews&m=read&o=137621543756b436f87e95c78211d5 |title=Pacific Islands News Association : PACNEWS - News reader |website=Pina.com.fj |date= |accessdate=2016-03-13 |archive-date=2016-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404215810/http://www.pina.com.fj/?p=pacnews&m=read&o=137621543756b436f87e95c78211d5 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，受关爱基里巴斯党新組成的的聯盟與前總統[[塞布羅羅·斯托|塞布羅羅·斯托]]支持<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/programmes/datelinepacific/audio/201788602/three-in-the-running-for-kiribati-presidential-election |title=Three in the running for Kiribati presidential election | Dateline Pacific, 6:05 am on 10 February 2016 | Radio New Zealand |website=Radionz.co.nz |date=2016-02-10 |accessdate=2016-03-13 |archive-date=2016-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215214330/http://www.radionz.co.nz/international/programmes/datelinepacific/audio/201788602/three-in-the-running-for-kiribati-presidential-election |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在此以前，他在2015年12月的[[議會_(吉里巴斯)|吉里巴斯議會]]選舉中重新當選為家鄉[[奧諾托阿環礁|奧諾托阿環礁]]的議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.parliament.gov.ki/sites/docs/newsletter/march.pdf |format=PDF |title=Maneaba Ni Maungatabu |website=Parliament.gov.ki |accessdate=2016-03-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020064644/http://www.parliament.gov.ki/sites/docs/newsletter/march.pdf |archivedate=2014-10-20 }}</ref>；也是斯托政府的財政部長。

